Do not call the Reset function unless it is required, fixes #76

Calling Reset when using threads will lead to some threads running
with the library's defaults which will cause crashes.

commit.message:
Disable LegacyStreamDisplay explicitly by default, make it configurable

This is done to match the change in the library in:
https://github.com/MediaArea/MediaInfoLib/commit/090e1476c8778b30b67572e55c446b0fc972eb65
and therefore included since MediaInfo v18.08.

The older behaviour can still be reproduced by setting
legacy_stream_display=True.
